p0519 = "May Christ our true God, through the prayers of his all pure and holy Mother, the intercessions of the holy glorious, all-praised Apostles, (of the Saint of the church and of the day) and of all the Saints, have mercy on us and save us, for he is good and loves mankind."
p0520 = "While the Christians kiss the Icon of the Mother of God, we chant the following Troparia."
